      "author": "davidvkimball",
      "description": "### Core Architecture & Refactoring\r\n- Observer Pattern Implementation: Introduced a SettingsObservable in src/main.ts. All services (e.g., BannerService, ImageProcessor, PasteHandler) now subscribe to this observable to receive settings updates. This has eliminated redundant updateSettings() boilerplate across src/main.ts.\r\n- API Key Migration: Added a secure migration process in src/main.ts that moves API keys (Pexels, Pixabay) from plaintext settings to Obsidian's secretStorage (for Obsidian versions 1.11.4+).\r\n\r\n### Dependency & Project Cleanup\r\n- Removed jiti: The jiti dependency has been removed from package.json.\r\n- .gitignore Updates: Refined to better manage project artifacts.",
