      "description": "### What's New\r\n\r\n- **Banner Images**: Display banner images from properties with device-specific settings (desktop, tablet, phone). Customize height, padding, border radius, fade effects, and optional icons. Courtesy of Simple Banner plugin.\r\n- **Obsidian Default Link Format**: New \"Obsidian default\" option for property links that automatically respects your Obsidian settings (`useMarkdownLinks`, `newLinkFormat`).\r\n\r\n### Improvements\r\n\r\n- Default property name changed to `\"banner\"` to align with banner feature\r\n- Fixed double border issue in settings view\r\n- Improved compatibility with older Obsidian versions\r\n- Various bug fixes and improvements",
